channel.title: Changing teleport names?
channel.description:
The teleports in the Modern spellbook in my server have normal RS names. How can I change a teleport name like Varrock teleport to Shops teleport, for example?
I've tried magicSpells.cfg and magicHandler.java, searched for Varrock, and found nothing. Any help?
